long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Updates the Google Omnibox to allow navigation directly any reddit user page without having to type in the entire URL.

Simply type 'u' and then a space into the navigation bar, at which point the /u/ Chrome extension will automatically pop into the bar. Type the name of the user to navigate to, hit enter, and the plugin will navigate to the correct page.
